------------------------------------------------------------- Array#each
     array.each {|item| block }   -&gt;   array

     From Ruby 1.9.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------
     Calls _block_ once for each element in _self_, passing that element
     as a parameter.

        a = [ "a", "b", "c" ]
        a.each {|x| print x, " -- " }

     produces:

        a -- b -- c --

sw@debian:~/sandbox$ </fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block id="id2548847"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:block margin-left="0pc" font-family="MetaPlusBold,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" keep-together.within-column="always"><fo:block keep-with-next.within-column="always"><fo:block font-family="MetaPlusBold" font-weight="bold" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before.minimum="1.8em" space-before.optimum="2.0em" space-before.maximum="2.2em" space-after.minimum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="0.1em" space-after.maximum="0.1em" text-align="left" start-indent="0pc"><fo:marker marker-class-name="section.head.marker">Hash</fo:marker><fo:block color="#000033" font-size="12.6pt">2.10.2. Hash</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Ein <fo:inline>„Hash“</fo:inline> ist eine Liste aus Schlüssel-/Wert-Paaren
      (key/value pairs). Ein Beispiel mit Strings als Schlüssel:<fo:block id="id2548861" text-align="start" wrap-option="wrap" hyphenation-character="\" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.maximum="1.2em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1.2em" hyphenate="true" white-space-collapse="false" white-space-treatment="preserve" linefeed-treatment="preserve" font-family="DejaVuSansMono" background-color="#FBFEDF" color="black" padding-left="12pt" padding-right="12pt" padding-top="6pt" padding-bottom="6pt" margin-left="0pc">sw@debian:~/sandbox$ <fo:inline font-weight="bold">irb</fo:inline>
irb(main):001:0&gt; <fo:inline font-weight="bold">preisliste = { '6 Eier' =&gt; 1.2, '12 Eier' =&gt; 2, '500 gr Butter' =&gt; 0.99 }</fo:inline>
