        folgende Felder hinzuzufügen:<fo:list-block id="id2550807" space-before.optimum="0.1pt" space-before.minimum="0.1pt" space-before.maximum="0.1pt" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em" provisional-label-separation="0.2em" provisional-distance-between-starts="1.0em"><fo:list-item id="id2550809" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block>•</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono">id:integer</fo:inline></fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Das ist die Unique-ID des Datensatzes. Das Feld wird von
              der Datenbank automatisch hochgezählt. Für alle SQL-Fans:
              AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL</fo:block></fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item id="id2550824" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block>•</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono">created_at:datetime</fo:inline></fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Das Feld wird von ActiveRecord automatisch beim Erstellen
              eines Datensatzes gefüllt.</fo:block></fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item id="id2550839" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block>•</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono">updated_at:datetime</fo:inline></fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Das Feld wird bei jeder Veränderung des Datensatzes
              automatisch an die aktuelle Zeit angepasst.</fo:block></fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item></fo:list-block></fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Am Anfang fragt man sich: "Muss das sein? Macht das wirklich
        Sinn?". Aber mit der Zeit lernt man diese automatisch gehandelten
        Felder schätzen.</fo:block></fo:block><fo:block id="migration-rollback"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:block margin-left="0pc" font-family="MetaPlusBold,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" keep-together.within-column="always"><fo:block keep-with-next.within-column="always"><fo:block font-family="MetaPlusBold" font-weight="bold" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before.minimum="1.8em" space-before.optimum="2.0em" space-before.maximum="2.2em" space-after.minimum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="0.1em" space-after.maximum="0.1em" text-align="left" start-indent="0pc"><fo:block color="#000033" font-size="11.7pt">3.4.3.2. Migration Rollback</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Es soll schon vorgekommen sein, das übereilt eine Migration
