MacBook:movie-app sw$</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block id="restful_datenbankzugriff_per_webbrowser"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:block margin-left="0pc" font-family="MetaPlusBold,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" keep-together.within-column="always"><fo:block keep-with-next.within-column="always"><fo:block font-family="MetaPlusBold" font-weight="bold" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before.minimum="1.8em" space-before.optimum="2.0em" space-before.maximum="2.2em" space-after.minimum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="0.1em" space-after.maximum="0.1em" text-align="left" start-indent="0pc"><fo:marker marker-class-name="section.head.marker">RESTful
      Datenbankzugriff per Webbrowser</fo:marker><fo:block color="#000033" font-size="12.6pt">3.4.4. RESTful
      Datenbankzugriff per Webbrowser</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Die Datenbank ist angelegt. Und der Vorteil von Scaffolding
      besteht darin, das wir jetzt auch direkt per Webbrowser in einer
      aktzeptablen Web-GUI darauf zugreifen können.</fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Gemäss der CRUD Idee (siehe <fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono"><fo:basic-link external-destination="url(http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/CRUD)">http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/CRUD</fo:basic-link></fo:inline>)
      bietet Rails dafür ein RESTful Webinterface an. Was heisst das? Sie
      können auf jede Resource innerhalb einer normalen Rails-Umgeben über
      definierte URLs zugreifen und damit folgende Datenbank-Operationen
      ausführen:<fo:list-block id="id2551021" space-before.optimum="0.1pt" space-before.minimum="0.1pt" space-before.maximum="0.1pt" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em" provisional-label-separation="0.2em" provisional-distance-between-starts="1.0em"><fo:list-item id="id2551023" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block>•</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block><fo:block>C für CREATE</fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">SQL: <fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono">INSERT INTO movies (title) VALUES ('Rain
            Man')</fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item id="id2551038" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block>•</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block><fo:block>R für READ</fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">SQL: <fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono">SELECT * FROM movies</fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item id="id2551052" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block>•</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block><fo:block>U für UPDATE</fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">SQL: <fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono">UPDATE movies SET title = 'Rain Man' WHERE id =
            1</fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item id="id2551067" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block>•</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block><fo:block>D für DELETE</fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">SQL: <fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono">DELETE FROM movies WHERE id = 1</fo:inline></fo:block></fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item></fo:list-block>Für den Rails-Neuling ist nicht direkt ersichtlich, wo
      den hier der grosse Vorteil liegt. Nachfolgend eine Mini-FAQ:<fo:block id="id2551085"><fo:block id="id2551087"><fo:block><fo:list-block provisional-label-separation="0.2em" space-before.optimum="0.1pt" space-before.minimum="0.1pt" space-before.maximum="0.1pt" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em" provisional-distance-between-starts="3em"><fo:list-item id="id2551090" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label id="id2551092" end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block font-weight="bold">1.</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Warum wird um das RESTful Interface in Ruby on Rails so
                ein Bohei gemacht?</fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label id="id2551102" end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block/></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Damit bekommt man ein sauberes und für alle
                Programmierer leicht verständliches Interface zu Ihrem System.
                Sie brauchen nur die URI
                <fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono">http://localhost:3000/movies</fo:inline> und das Wissen, das es
                sich um ein RESTful Webdienst handelt und Sie können direkt
                loslegen.</fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item id="id2551120" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label id="id2551122" end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block font-weight="bold">2.</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Ist RESTful nur für die automatische Abfrage zwischen
                Computern gut?</fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label id="id2551132" end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block/></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Nein. RESTful ist auch ein guter Denkansatz, um URLs und
                damit ganze Webseiten strukturierter zu gestalten.</fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item id="id2551143" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label id="id2551145" end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block font-weight="bold">3.</fo:block></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Ist RESTful Teil der <fo:inline font-style="italic">Convention over
                Configuration</fo:inline> Idee?</fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item><fo:list-item space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1em"><fo:list-item-label id="id2551158" end-indent="label-end()"><fo:block/></fo:list-item-label><fo:list-item-body start-indent="body-start()"><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Ja! Jeder Rails-Entwickler kann sich so in kurzer Zeit
                in ein ihm neues Rails-Projekt einarbeiten.</fo:block></fo:list-item-body></fo:list-item></fo:list-block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block id="id2551172"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:block margin-left="0pc" font-family="MetaPlusBold,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" keep-together.within-column="always"><fo:block keep-with-next.within-column="always"><fo:block font-family="MetaPlusBold" font-weight="bold" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before.minimum="1.8em" space-before.optimum="2.0em" space-before.maximum="2.2em" space-after.minimum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="0.1em" space-after.maximum="0.1em" text-align="left" start-indent="0pc"><fo:block color="#000033" font-size="11.7pt">3.4.4.1. Start des Webservers</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Als erstes starten wir wie immer mit rails server unseren
