</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block id="id2552036"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:block margin-left="0pc" font-family="MetaPlusBold,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" keep-together.within-column="always"><fo:block keep-with-next.within-column="always"><fo:block font-family="MetaPlusBold" font-weight="bold" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before.minimum="1.8em" space-before.optimum="2.0em" space-before.maximum="2.2em" space-after.minimum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="0.1em" space-after.maximum="0.1em" text-align="left" start-indent="0pc"><fo:block color="#000033" font-size="11.7pt">3.4.6.3. show</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block space-before.minimum="0.1em" space-before.optimum="0.1em" space-before.maximum="0.1em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.maximum="1.2em">Einen einzelnen Film kann man sich mit der ID des Eintrages
        (hier die 1) und der entsprechenden URL <fo:inline font-family="DejaVuSansMono"><fo:basic-link external-destination="url(http://0.0.0.0:3000/movies/1.xml)">http://0.0.0.0:3000/movies/1.xml</fo:basic-link></fo:inline>
        anschauen. <fo:block id="id2552053" text-align="start" wrap-option="wrap" hyphenation-character="\" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.maximum="1.2em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1.2em" hyphenate="true" white-space-collapse="false" white-space-treatment="preserve" linefeed-treatment="preserve" font-family="DejaVuSansMono" background-color="#FBFEDF" color="black" padding-left="12pt" padding-right="12pt" padding-top="6pt" padding-bottom="6pt" margin-left="0pc">MacBook:~ sw$ <fo:inline font-weight="bold">curl -X GET -H 'Content-Type: application/xml' http://0.0.0.0:3000/movies/1.xml</fo:inline>
